Sears, Roebuck and Co said retail salesof its Merchandise Group in March rose 4.2 pct to 2.62 billiondlrs from 2.51 billion dlrs a year ago.    For the nine weeks ended April Four, Sears MerchandiseGroup sales rose 4.5 pct to 4.46 billion dlrs from 4.27 billiondlrs in the same 1986 period. Reuter&#3;